and more importantly, the Genie.

85
00:04:48,950 --> 00:04:51,300
現在我非常好奇
Now this has got me quite curious.

86
00:04:53,020 --> 00:04:55,640
如果有誰能告訴他們去哪了
If only someone could tell me where they went.

87
00:04:56,820 --> 00:04:59,010
