I don't know where he went.

97
00:05:23,770 --> 00:05:25,510
但他把塞勒斯也帶走了
But he brought Cyrus with him.

98
00:05:28,950 --> 00:05:30,530
親愛的  這籠子已經破了
Darling, the cage has been cut open.

99
00:05:30,530 --> 00:05:33,090
賈法爾想帶他走  用鑰匙就可以了
If Jafar wanted to take him, he'd have used the key!

100
00:05:34,350 --> 00:05:37,290
無所謂  你永遠抓不到他
It doesn't matter. You will never catch him.

101
00:05:37,290 --> 00:05:38,210
為什么
Why is that?

102
00:05:38,500 --> 00:05:42,760
