All I have to do is follow the sun west

107
00:06:41,340 --> 00:06:42,710
就能找到你
and I'll find you.

108
00:06:44,300 --> 00:06:45,590
堅持住  愛麗絲
Stay strong, Alice.

109
00:06:46,100 --> 00:06:47,370
