They say it's so dark,

117
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:10,310
連自己的鼻子都看不到
you can't even find your own nose.

118
00:07:11,910 --> 00:07:13,940
我決定碰碰運氣  謝了
I'll take my chances. Thank you.

119
00:07:14,210 --> 00:07:16,400
這樣做似乎很冒險  對吧
That seems awful dangerous, don't it?

120
00:07:16,900 --> 00:07:19,380
一個女孩獨自出行
A little girl traveling alone.

121
