A little bit of darkness won't hurt anybody.

190
00:11:38,220 --> 00:11:40,050
該死的  我的頭
Bloody hell, my head.

191
00:11:42,090 --> 00:11:43,780
拜托  老兄  能讓我喝口水嗎
Please, mate, can I get a sip of that water?

192
00:11:43,780 --> 00:11:46,560
你沒事吧  看起來氣色不好
Are you okay? You don't look too good.

193
00:11:46,690 --> 00:11:47,790
你被石化過嗎
You ever been stoned?

