What are these?

603
00:35:09,300 --> 00:35:10,680
放開我  讓我走
Get off me! Let me go!

604
00:35:11,440 --> 00:35:13,860
就是這樣  棒極了  愛麗絲
Yes, that's it. Bloody brilliant, Alice!

605
00:35:14,200 --> 00:35:15,630
