We both know she couldn't stay here.

613
00:36:31,570 --> 00:36:33,280
她在那里會更開心的
She's going to be much happier.

614
00:36:34,300 --> 00:36:36,010
所以你覺得她是做出了正確的選擇
So you think she made the right decision?

615
00:36:36,430 --> 00:36:37,710
我知道她做對了
I know she did.

616
00:36:38,080 --> 00:36:40,170
我為她的聰明感到驚訝
I was actually surprised at her wisdom.

617
00:36:44,000 --> 00:36:45,780
都會好起來的
It's going to be fine.

618
00:36:46,150 --> 00:36:48,250
她不能永遠做一個小女孩  埃德溫
She can't be a little girl forever, Edwin,

619
00:36:48,530 --> 00:36:50,460
而且醫生會好好照顧她的
And he'll take excellent care of her.

620
00:36:52,040 --> 00:36:53,400
我也希望如此
I certainly hope so.

621
00:37:31,290 --> 00:37:33,960
她甚至都不想我到醫院去看她
She doesn't even want me to visit the hospital, you know.

622
00:37:34,130 --> 00:37:36,280
她還太過年輕魯莽
She's still young and impetuous,

623
00:37:36,660 --> 00:37:38,220
所以這樣對她來說才是最好的
which is why this is best.

624
00:37:38,500 --> 00:37:40,270
是時候讓她成長起來了
It's time for her to grow up.

